headline: UNC Health Southeastern Taps Transact + CBORD to Launch Mobile Meal Ordering
summary: SCOTTSDALE, Ariz., July 23, 2025--Transact + CBORD today announced the implementation of a new self-service meal ordering capability at UNC Health Southeastern. Powered by the CBORD® Patient App, the new offering enhances the patient experience by providing greater autonomy, interactive nutrition education, and an easier way for patients and their loved ones to participate in care.
